  "body": "### Version of Hardhat\n\n2.12.7\n\n### What happened?\n\nI ran this command:\r\n\r\n```\r\n/Users/me/path/to/hardhat node --hostname 127.0.0.1 --port 8545 --config /Users/me/.ape/hardhat/hardhat.config.js --show-stack-traces\r\n```\r\n\r\nand my config looks like this:\r\n\r\n```yaml\r\n// See https://hardhat.org/config/ for config options.\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  networks: {\r\n    hardhat: {\r\n      hardfork: \"shanghai\",\r\n      // Base fee of 0 allows use of 0 gas price when testing\r\n      initialBaseFeePerGas: 0,\r\n      accounts: {\r\n        mnemonic: \"test test test test test test test test test test test junk\",\r\n        path: \"m/44'/60'/0'\",\r\n        count: 10\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n  },\r\n};\r\n```\r\n\r\nand I get this error:\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\n  * Invalid value {\"hardfork\":\"shanghai\",\"initialBaseFeePerGas\":0,\"accounts\":{\"mnemonic\":\"test test test test test test test test test test test junk\",\"path\":\"m/44'/60'/0'\",\"count\":10}} for HardhatConfig.networks.hardhat - Expected a value of type HardhatNetworkConfig.\r\n  * Unexpected config HardhatConfig.networks.hardhat.initialBaseFeePerGas found - This field is only valid for networks with EIP-1559. Try a newer hardfork or remove it.\r\n\r\nTo learn more about Hardhat's configuration, please go to https://hardhat.org/config/\r\n    at validateConfig (/Users/me/ApeProjects/yearn-vaults-v3/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/config/config-validation.ts:367:9)\r\n    at loadConfigAndTasks (/Users/me/ApeProjects/yearn-vaults-v3/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/config/config-loading.ts:94:17)\r\n    at main (/Users/me/ApeProjects/yearn-vaults-v3/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/cli/cli.ts:199:62)\r\n```\n\n### Minimal reproduction steps\n\n1. Create a config same as from What Happened in a hidden dir in your home dir\r\n2. Run the command from the *What happened* section\r\n\n\n### Search terms\n\nconfig hardfork shanghai basefee gas",
